# Service TypeScript

- Preserve JWT validation and all currently accepted app roles.
- Connect to Postgres with the non-owner application login and keep RLS enforced.
- Build deployment bundles into ignored `.artifacts/deploy/`; preserve the
  import-meta bootstrap required for function registration.
- Keep CORS on the Function App and configuration in app settings.
- Read `docs/operations/live-environment.md` before live reads. Diagnosis is
  read-only; production changes require the implementation owner and approval.
